site.projectname.util

Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • site.projectname.util.Logger

  • public class Logger
extends java.lang.Object
    Used across the program to generate logs. Created logs are automagically stored in Logger.logs Used to log arbitrary information into a timestamped file. File can be located in the Logs directory They are further sorted into directories according to the creator (given in the constructor)
    Since:
    2015-5-24
